Drill Switchover Activity steps:

step 1 : DNS Switchover from DC to DR.

step 2 : Stop the application at DC side.
		 will ran our script at bastian server.

step 3&4 : Database switchover from DC to DR.

step 3&4 : Perform the Kafka Clean-up Activity at DC side.
			 cd /opt/kafka/bin/
			./kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list
		
			for t in $(./kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list | grep -v '^__' | grep -v 'mm2-' | grep -v 'mirrormaker2-'); do
			echo "Deleting topic: $t"
			./kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --delete --topic "$t"
			done
			exit

step 5 : Swap the routes in Git-lab of both DC and DR.
			Update DC & DR (Reverse Direction)


step 6 : Brought up the application at DR side.
		 will ran our script at bastian server

step 7 : Check the application status and Kafka.
		 Verify MM2 Logs
		 Validate Topic Sync
		 cd /opt/kafka/bin/
		./kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list
		exit
=======
